criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Venous thromboembolism (thrombosis in the deep venous system of upper or lower
             extremities or iliac veins and/or pulmonary embolism) as detected by ultrasonography,
             phlebography, computer tomography, or angiography;

          -  > 18 years or older;

          -  Written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  > 2 days after VTE diagnosis;

          -  No blood withdrawal at baseline
